service.tut.pori.contentanalysis

Class AnalysisBackend

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.tut.pori.contentanalysis.AnalysisBackend

  • public class AnalysisBackend
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains details of a single analysis back-end.

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<backend>
  <url>http://example.org/xtvkknUPsuCVeWmdFHia</url>
  <backendId>1511089081</backendId>
  <description>qgLrxrfiThZLXfDGkVYwwJPHsBGwWducXDosYxqPjQrXaWRnHfCszwuOqciMgkOr</description>
  <enabled>true</enabled>
  <capabilityList>
    <capability>PHOTO_ANALYSIS</capability>
    <capability>PHOTO_SEARCH</capability>
    <capability>USER_FEEDBACK</capability>
    <capability>VIDEO_ANALYSIS</capability>
    <capability>VIDEO_SEARCH</capability>
  </capabilityList>
</backend>
